Usage: trendbot [INSTR]

Trading bot that collects past trades to send a matching trade.

  -H, --host=NAME       Connect to NAME.
  -d, --daemonise       Detach from terminal.
  -F, --freq=I          Collect trades over a period of I.
  --max=P               Maximum position, default: unlimited.
  -Q, --qty=Q           Threshold quantity, default: 1000
  --contrarian          Go against the trend.
